    "faq_with_image_m73Xra": {
      "type": "faq-with-image",
      "blocks": {
        "accordion_GhRGXt": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "settings": {
            "accordion_header": "What can I expect during my initial consultation?",
            "open_by_default": false,
            "text": "<p>Your first consultation is a relaxed, collaborative meeting. You will sit down one-on-one with an expert designer to:</p><ul><li>Discuss your inspiration, style, and budget.</li><li>View examples from our collection.</li><li>Look at a curated selection of diamonds or gemstones.</li><li>Begin sketching out initial ideas for your bespoke piece.</li></ul><p>For bespoke designs, this is the first step in our 3D CAD design process, where we bring your vision to life.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "accordion_HmVJLJ": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "settings": {
            "accordion_header": "What should I bring or prepare for my appointment?",
            "open_by_default": false,
            "text": "<p>The most helpful thing you can bring is your imagination! If you have any inspirational images (from Pinterest, magazines, or photos), please bring them along. It's also useful to have a clear idea of your budget range, as this helps our designers make the best possible recommendations for you.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "accordion_xFhTbU": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "settings": {
            "accordion_header": "Am I under any obligation to make a purchase after my consultation?",
            "open_by_default": false,
            "text": "<p>Absolutely not. Our consultations are genuinely no-obligation. We are here to provide expert advice and help you understand your options. We want you to feel 100% confident and excited before moving forward with any design or repair.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "accordion_pxHnfz": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "settings": {
            "accordion_header": "Do I need an appointment, or can I just walk into the showroom?",
            "open_by_default": false,
            "text": "<p>You are always welcome to visit our showroom during opening hours to browse our collection. However, we highly recommend booking an appointment for a design consultation or complex repair. An appointment ensures that a designer is reserved exclusively for you, giving you their undivided time and attention.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "accordion_BRezAN": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "settings": {
            "accordion_header": "How long should I set aside for my appointment?",
            "open_by_default": false,
            "text": "<p>We recommend setting aside about one hour for your consultation. This gives us ample time to discuss your ideas in detail, answer all your questions, and explore different design possibilities without you feeling rushed.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
